                       Welcome to RelayBot
               A simple multi-protocol chat relay bot.

DESCRIPTION:
This program is designed as a simple in game chat relay service. It is
currently capable of relaying IRC messages and Minecraft chat messages.

REQUIREMENTS:
Requires at the very least Python 3.4

INSTALLATION:
Installation is simple, once downloaded you need only copy
conf/exampleconfig.xml to conf/config.xml, read the enclosed comments
and configure as necesary. After completing conf/config.xml you will then be
able to run the bot using 'python run.py'

CONTACT/SUPPORT:
If you need any help, support or just want to say thanks, feel free to drop
by the IRC channel #minecraft on irc.afternet.org
